playstore_details.title: Stealth Browser - Fast Private
playstore_details.description:
Stealth BrowserThe original Stealth Browser is back! Stealth Browser is a super fast, private, ad-free mobile browser for Android. If you want the private browsing experience with no ads and super quick speeds, then Stealth Browser is for you!
Features:
Super Fast
Built to be fast so you’re never left waiting for pages to load. By utilizing the WebKit rendering engine that comes built into your Android device, we can ensure a fast browsing experience that won't disappoint.
Private
Stealth Private Browser opens by default in incognito mode to keep your browsing private and without a footprint. Download Orbot and turn on proxy support to mask your identify and location, use StartPage or DuckDuckGo for your search engine, or disable settings that you think leave you at risk.
No Ads
Don’t like ads popping up when you’re surfing the net? Neither do we. We have an in-built Ad-Blocker which is on by default so you don't ever have to see see an ad again!
Secure Autofill
We’ve teamed up with Fillr to provide a seamless integration of their amazing and secure autofill technology. Fillr makes filling forms and transacting on your mobile a breeze.
Small & Light
Our app is 90% smaller and lighter than Chrome, ensuring fast downloading, installing and updating along with smooth running of your device.
Great Design
Stealth Browser's interface was carefully crafted so you can browse as efficiently as possible without sacrificing those features that mean the most to you. Tabs and Bookmarks are all tucked neatly away in side drawers, only a swipe away, allowing maximum screen viewing with minimal interference from the browser's navigation bar.
Other Features:
- Full Screen
- Inverted Rendering
- Search Suggestions
- Bookmarks
- History
- User Agents
- Open Source
- Plus much more…

Stealth Browser is based on webkit and equipped with a great number of users across more than 139 countries and regions.
